    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once the pan is hot, add your <strong>roasted garlic paste </strong>and <strong>halved cherry tomatoes </strong>and cook for 3-4 min until the tomatoes have started to break down</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2417Step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
