            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>quick cook spaghetti</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the spaghetti is cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Remove from the heat and drain, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong>, then return to the pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and set aside until later</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1605778904590-x200.jpg",
