            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen<strong> </strong>paper and dress with your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>in a bowl – this is your<strong> dressed salad</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
