            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tomato & olive sauce</strong> over the <strong>cooked spaghetti </strong>with the <strong>dressed salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> and sprinkle over the <strong>caper crumb</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
